usage: audit_humanize_generation_qualification.py [-h]
                                                  [--skill-root SKILL_ROOT]
                                                  [--requirements REQUIREMENTS]
                                                  [--contract CONTRACT]
                                                  [--artifact-root ARTIFACT_ROOT]
                                                  [--replay-timeout REPLAY_TIMEOUT]
                                                  [--format {json,text}]
                                                  [--output OUTPUT]
                                                  [manifest]

Audit current forward-generation qualification evidence. A missing manifest is
an honest NOT_EVALUATED audit, not a PASS.

positional arguments:
  manifest              strict JSON evidence manifest

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --skill-root SKILL_ROOT
  --requirements REQUIREMENTS
  --contract CONTRACT
  --artifact-root ARTIFACT_ROOT
                        root for all manifest-relative evidence paths;
                        defaults to the manifest directory
  --replay-timeout REPLAY_TIMEOUT
  --format {json,text}
  --output OUTPUT       optional report path outside the Skill root
